verbose_text: The consumption of fluoride resulted in severe fluorosis and in an impaired OC function [impaired bone resorption, and a low mRNA expression of nuclear factor of activated T-cells 1 (NFATc1), ATPase H + transporting V0 subunit D2 (ATP6v0d2) and osteopetrosis associated trans-membrane protein 1 (Ostm1)].
evidence: expression of nuclear factor of activated T-cells 1
